title: Piano Professor Peter Takács to Perform at Carnegie Hall (Oberlin College)
text: ( Source : Oberlin College ) ( Photo by Tanya Rosen-Jones '97) Peter Takács, an esteemed professor of piano at Oberlin for 39 years, will launch a new series of performances at Carnegie Hall ’s Weill Recital Hall beginning Sunday, October 18 .
